jobs.description:
Are you an analytical thinker? Do you know how to be detail-oriented and want to work in a Multi-Family Office?
We’re looking for an intern to:
• help analysts with investment analysis of assets and portfolio construction;
• help in the daily routine of fund management;
• collaborate with the analysts to produce client and fund’s monthly reports
• participate in the internal committees for economic scenario discussion and investment strategy definition

